             was indicted for <rs id="t18230409-209-off1118" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18230409-209-off1118" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18230409-209-off1118" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18230409-209-cd1119" type="crimeDate">14th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-209-off1118 t18230409-209-cd1119"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230409-209-off1120 t18230409-209-cd1119"></join>, a spoon, value 12 s.; two bottles, value 6 d.; two quarts of wine, value 10 s.; 6 lbs. of bread, value 1 s.; half an ounce of tea, value 3 d.; one ounce of cocoa, value 2 d.; three pair of gloves, value 2 s.; seven plates, value 3 s., and four ounces of mutton, value 2 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18230409-209-victim1865" type="victimName">
                  William Croft 
                  Fish
               <interp inst="t18230409-209-victim1865" type="surname" value="Fish"></interp>
